>"},{"pid":"359ba0d94f362f7516bd982d4b321e9192d48ede","tid":1797832,"uid":330204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5b21254f06c21c0f16739f027f02b4c5f79e95b2","tid":1797832,"uid":159913,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T17:46:19.000Z","msg":"用github我以為你想搵人由頭寫open source筆記<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁樣唔會有版權問題，但好chur<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T17:52:16.000Z","msg":"其實本身係諗住純 GitHub<br />\n<br />\n但係諗返起好似有 Github Page 呢樣嘢。<br />\n<br />\n所以而家就搞成噉。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n個計畫有分兩個部分，一個係開源教科書，另一個係筆記。<br />\n<br />\n筆記嗰邊靠收集，要睇下有冇人肯貢獻。<br />\n<br />\n教科書嗰邊未諗到點做。<br />\n其中一個諗法係將最多人贊同嘅嗰堆筆記整合。<br />\n<br />\n從頭寫過又唔係唔得嘅，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不過有人肯做咩。"},{"pid":"c8128f2f93c094dd580e40b2f9bb9dae136b4844","tid":1797832,"uid":330204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5b21254f06c21c0f16739f027f02b4c5f79e95b2","tid":1797832,"uid":159913,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T17:46:19.000Z","msg":"用github我以為你想搵人由頭寫open source筆記<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁樣唔會有版權問題，但好chur<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T17:59:52.000Z","msg":"欸其實你咁講又好似唔錯。<br />\n<br />\n試下開個純 GitHub 嘅 open source 筆記。<br />\n<br />\n等陣。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 啲人唔識用 GitHub（爆喊"},{"pid":"5548ad953bb20c587c859cb29912a41ed6f52a43","tid":1797832,"uid":222614,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T21:35:33.000Z","msg":"支持但呢啲學術野可唔可以用返英文？<br />\n<br />\n中文睇到一舊舊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c1b6b8c068df86a59ba07b28df25daa2cf4c2e1","t