r 算啦<br />\ngithub係for code-based file versioning<br />\n如果人手重打做markdown，都仲值得再整個frontend去食github raw<br />\n但得圖片/pdf 就咪搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T12:19:37.000Z","msg":"ok  冷水收到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\ngoogle drive 可以畀人 upload 咩<br />\n<br />\n其實我都 feel 搞唔起。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee90d56714812f66657fadb9d40550e8efbc88c6","tid":1797832,"uid":330204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T13:33:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我當我自己整咗個整合資源嘅 Page 啦。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b962091a4b6aec211d0cc1418c86d6fa4919f41","tid":1797832,"uid":232077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ee90d56714812f66657fadb9d40550e8efbc88c6","tid":1797832,"uid":330204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T13:33:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我當我自己整咗個整合資源嘅 Page 啦。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T18:51:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"401b666dd2089c5b2a918fc8cd9ab4fed16d94e0","tid":1797832,"uid":29218,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T07:39:08.000Z","msg":"我六七年前都有諗過做類似project<br />\n我想整晒全港所有科目小一至中六嘅開源教科書<br />\n不過喺佔領運動後擱置了<br />\n<br />\n我提議分三部份<br />\n1. 教科書<br />\n2. 題目/試卷<br />\n3. 答題貼士/解題<br />\n<br />\n首先筆記無乜用 特別係其他人嘅手寫筆記 好難check啱唔啱<br />\n整做png/pdf 都好麻煩 最好係整合成答題貼士<br />\nformat 方面可以參考 wiki 用LaTeX<br />\n題目/試卷 同 答題貼士/解題 可以慢慢積累<br />\n<br />\n要一個人做晒係無可能 要做所有科都係<br />\n如果你想專攻DSE<br />\n我建議係由淺入手 先做一科數學科<br />\n因為數學係最易知題目/答案啱唔啱<br />\n數學又係必修科<br />\n同埋全世界嘅數學科都係差不多 網上好多資源<br />\n分分鐘搵到海外高手一齊搞<br />\n如果集合到一班有心人<br />\n唔使好耐就可以出到第一版教科書"},{"pid":"6b932b217c499ca2c9f5d94637c6320946a6fe44","tid":1797832,"uid":131836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T07:48:53.000Z","msg":"點確定入面d野係岩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以前有學生買左d 聲稱5**手抄筆記返黎<br />\nd concept 錯撚晒<br />\n都唔知係咪用黎伏人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42d9bba7c694d68718fbd3af99fa3135655ab0a6","tid":1797832,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6b932b217c499ca2c9f5d94637c6320946a6fe44","tid":1797832,"uid":131836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T07:48:53.000Z","msg":"點確定入面d野係岩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以前有學生買左d 聲稱5**手抄筆記返黎<br />\nd concept 錯撚晒<br />\n都唔知係咪用黎伏人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T08:09:52.000Z","msg":"5**其實唔代表Concept好<br />\n可能有啲人靠操卷操返嚟"},{"pid":"dc7b2ecd9ec5e794195de1f56e7149fdcba11361","tid":1797832,"uid":131836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"42d9bba7c694d68718fbd3af99fa3135655ab0a6","tid":1797832,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6b932b217c499ca2c9f5d94637c6320946a6fe44","tid":1797832,"uid":131836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T07:48:53.000Z","msg":"點確定入面d野係岩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以前有學生買左d 聲稱5**手抄筆記返黎<br />\nd concept 錯撚晒<br />\n都唔知係咪用黎伏人<i